{"tid":2304759,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭楊潤雄政治行先 為左”4/12 國家憲法日”堅拒停課","createTime":"2020-11-29T05:47:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T04:47:23.000Z","uid":123774,"like":11,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"64587bd470d0121cb38235dd108662a49d69953e","tid":2304759,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T05:47:58.000Z","msg":"首先唔好用考試做理由<br />\n之前已經做過停課學生淨係返學校考試<br />\n仲有本身12月好多學校都係考緊試<br />\n無啦啦彈張通告攪國家洗腦日<br />\n<br />\n依家單日過百單都唔肯停課<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558759-20201106.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558759-20201106.htm&d=7TTtdOR49HUCBqTToLMoR8fSVjQS2PdSygdC4qSdyAU%3D&h=1fa88db8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558759-20201106.htm&h=2b64242e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558759-20201106.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n通告:<br />\n<a href=\"https://applications.edb.gov.hk/circular/upload/EDBCM/EDBCM20166C.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapplications.edb.gov.hk%2Fcircular%2Fupload%2FEDBCM%2FEDBCM20166C.pdf&d=7TTtdOR49HUCBqTToLMoR8fSVjQS2PdSygdC4qSdyAU%3D&h=21a22977\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://applications.edb.gov.hk/circular/upload/EDBCM/EDBCM20166C.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n教育局向中小學發通告，首次為12月4日「國家憲法日」學校舉行的推廣活動，提供相關資料和活動建議。教育局回覆查詢時表示，鼓勵學校按校情及教學情況，適切安排校本教育活動，促進學生全面認識《憲法》和《基本法》，培養國民身分認同。<br />\n<br />\n通告建議學校，在12月4日「國家憲法日」升掛國旗、區旗及奏唱國歌時，教職員及學生要遵守相關禮儀。另外，亦就《憲法》和《基本法》舉行全方位學習活動。"},{"pid":"59e063a7bb6340486f65433f4bc8326fd83847f9","tid":2304759,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T05:50:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88c1e1a7471f3ab06fa60a4c7d3d6132a9be6ab1","tid":2304759,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T05:58:13.